Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-khen-ngoi-1-cau-thu-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-uzbekistan-168-193977.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 Uzbekistan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-u23-viet-nam-nuoi-tiec-vi-khong-doi-no-duoc-uzbekistan-168-193975.html\">Sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Uzbekistan?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\">Tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu, HLV Park Hang Seo lo \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee7 quan</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5218","checkdouble":"193981"},{"date":"22:08 07/08","title":"V\u1eeba t\u1edbi PSG, Buffon \u0111\u00e3 \"kh\u00e9o n\u1ecbnh\" Mbappe","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/vua-toi-psg-buffon-da-kheo-ninh-mbappe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Paris m\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u2013 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Buffon ca ng\u1ee3i Mbappe sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c th\u1eddi gian qua.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nBuffon h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u00e0n em<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00edt g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi Mbappe trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Buffon r\u1ea5t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng tu\u1ed5i con m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd v\u1ee5t s\u00e1ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1eeba t\u1edbi PSG, Buffon ca ng\u1ee3i Mbappe h\u1ebft l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1eeba t\u1edbi PSG, Buffon ca ng\u1ee3i Mbappe h\u1ebft l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/bakayoko-mbappe-la-cau-thu-tot-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Buffon ca ng\u1ee3i Mbappe s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Monaco tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Andrea Barzagli, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng trong su\u1ed1t 20 n\u0103m s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ebfm khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 r\u1eb1ng Barzagli r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Mbappe.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft khi Barzagli t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf Mbappe th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hy v\u1ecdng Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t, khi\u00eam nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng kh\u00e1t khao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u00e0 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean nh\u1eefng trang s\u1eed \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Buffon ca ng\u1ee3i Mbappe.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/vo-dich-world-cup-mbappe-da-bat-dau-lam-thuong-hieu-197-192156.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/bakayoko-mbappe-la-cau-thu-tot-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/vo-dich-world-cup-mbappe-da-bat-dau-lam-thuong-hieu-197-192156.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u</span><br>\r\nS\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 29 nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Kylian Mbappe ch\u1ecdn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/danh-sach-cau-thu-hay-nhat-nam-cua-fifa-mbappe-sanh-vai-cung-ronaldo-messi-184-191953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/danh-sach-cau-thu-hay-nhat-nam-cua-fifa-mbappe-sanh-vai-cung-ronaldo-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/danh-sach-cau-thu-hay-nhat-nam-cua-fifa-mbappe-sanh-vai-cung-ronaldo-messi-184-191953.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a FIFA: Mbappe s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Ronaldo, Messi</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Kylian Mbappe s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a FIFA.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5217","checkdouble":"193971"},{"date":"21:42 07/08","title":"Liverpool 3-1 Torino: Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/liverpool-vs-torino-tran-dau-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, \"L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf\" v\u00f9ng Merseyside kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i qu\u00e2n xanh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Serie A tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Anfield.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: LIVERPOOL 3-1 TORINO\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/8/Liverpool-vs-Torino.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund \u1edf IC Cup 2018, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh  kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Man City, M.U  v\u00e0 Napoli. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng v\u1edbi HLV Jurgen Klopp l\u00e0 c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 (c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1eabn  d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb) \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. B\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb3ng Sadio Mane, Salah v\u00e0  Firmino \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng  kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m.\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<p>D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Liverpool \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a  tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 chu\u1ed7i 8 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i  g\u1eb7p Torino, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 24 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng,  th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u00e0 ngay t\u1eeb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng  c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 (\u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a Liverpool)  l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec1u.</p>\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Torino r\u00f5  r\u00e0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thua k\u00e9m 4 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. D\u00f9 Il Toro \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng  trong 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n to\u00e0n d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea7m (Pro Patria,  Renate, Nice, Chapecoense). Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia,  HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n  di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a tam t\u1ea5u M-S-F. \u0110\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 l\u00e0 si\u00eau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t  h\u00e0nh tinh: Alisson Becker.</p>\r\n<p>Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa do Wijnaldum c\u00f9ng hai t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y:  Fabinho vs Keita ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 do trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 Van Dijk ch\u1ec9 huy v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1  c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi anh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Phillips trong khi hai c\u00e1nh do ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n l\u1edbn m\u00f9a  tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Arnold c\u00f9ng Moreno cai qu\u1ea3n. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u1ee7ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ti\u1ebfp  t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ea5y may tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, The Kop \u00e0o l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng sau ti\u1ebfng  c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c song Torino c\u0169ng ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat th\u1ee9 8, Arnold t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 v\u00e0 Salah  ch\u00fat n\u1eefa ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf. Ph\u00fat 16,  Salah gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Torino r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng cho Mane b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c \u00e1p s\u00e1t  khung th\u00e0nh song ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mali kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t di\u1ec3m th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n v\u00ec b\u1ecb can  thi\u1ec7p tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p. \u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, \"L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf\" \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ebfc thay, ti\u1ec1n  v\u1ec7 t\u00e2n binh Fabinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 ra ngo\u00e0i tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 21 th\u00ec Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb  Salah, Firmino b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Torino r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi  \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia. V\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u0103ng. Ch\u00ednh Firmino ch\u1ecdc khe  thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Wijnaldum tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u00fat quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Sirigu, th\u1ee7  th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG.</p>\r\n<p>B\u1ecb \u00e9p s\u00e2n v\u00e0 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n song trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u00e9t \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n  c\u1ee7a Serie A \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh c\u1ee7a Belotti, ng\u00f4i  sao s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn d\u00f2m ng\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trung  th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi Torino. Nh\u1edd b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb  \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 l\u00e9p v\u1ebf so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<p>Ph\u00fat 40, Fabinho x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Torino nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sirigu trong  pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u00fat n\u1ed1i sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng tr\u00fang ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i  ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eadt ra. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1. Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao,  HLV Klopp thay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, chuy\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn  giao h\u1eefu, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Premier League 2018/19 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi  tranh.</p>\r\n<p>D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh trong hi\u1ec7p 2 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7p 1 nh\u01b0ng Liverpool v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm  \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u th\u1ebf, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu do khao kh\u00e1t th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u1eb7c s\u1ebd  ph\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb m\u00f9a t\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i theo di\u1ec7n cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n hay b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t.  Tuy v\u1eady, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eabn \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u suy gi\u1ea3m so v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 1. Ph\u00fat 57,  Sturridge kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf qu\u00e1 ng\u1ecdt \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i r\u1ed3i co  ch\u00e2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0103ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Torino.</p>\r\nKh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00f3, Danny Ings tuy \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Torino v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3  tung ra pha k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho  Liverpool. Ph\u00fat 66, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 Alisson \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \"\u0111\u1ed9ng th\u1ee7\" sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh  hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh c\u1ee7a Torino. Sau \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u0169ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n  nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Karius, th\u1ea7n g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a b\u1ecb t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 kh\u1ecfi Anfield  sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0  l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn The Kop ph\u1ea3i chi ti\u1ec1n t\u1ea5n cho Alisson. <br>\r\n<p>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ph\u00fat 87 khi Shaqiri b\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng  c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba cho Sturridge b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u1edbi phong  \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Sturridge h\u1eb3n  s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra cho HLV Klopp c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u nho nh\u1ecf. Tuy r\u1eb1ng, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi  Anh \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf song n\u1ebfu c\u00e1i  t\u00ean n\u00e0o trong tam t\u1ea5u M-F-S suy gi\u1ea3m phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00ec ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng th\u1eddi c\u01a1 s\u1ebd t\u1edbi  v\u1edbi Sturridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua 1/13 tr\u1eadn, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/18 m\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao nh\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Premier League sau 30 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nLiverpool: Alisson; Alexander-Arnold, Van Dijk, Phillips, Moreno; Fabinho,  Wijnaldum, Keita; Mane, Salah, Firmino<br>\r\nTorino: Sirigu, Bremer, Izzo, Nkoulou, De Silvestri; Rincon, Baselli; Meite,  Berenguer, Falque; Belotti.</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5216","checkdouble":"193966"},{"date":"03:00 08/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Real Madrid vs Roma 07h05 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/real-madrid-vs-roma-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Real Madrid vs Roma: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs AS Roma gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 07h05 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 8/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>DANH S\u00c1CH XU\u1ea4T PH\u00c1T<br>\r\nReal Madrid (4-3-3):</strong> Keylor Navas; Dani Carvajal, Sergio Ramos, Nacho Fernandez, Sergio Reguilon; Dani Ceballos, Toni Kroos, Isco; Gareth Bale, Karim Benzema, Marco Asensio.<br>\r\n<strong>Roma (4-3-3): </strong>Robin Olsen, Alessandro Florenzi, Federico Fazio, Ivan Marcano, Aleksandar Kolarov; Bryan Cristante, Daniele De Rossi, Javier Pastore; Stephan El Shaarawy, Edin Dzeko, Diego Perotti. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>TH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH</h2>\r\n- Real: V\u1eafng Varane, Marcelo, Casemiro v\u00e0 Modric.<br>\r\n- Roma: C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n- Theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Real th\u1eafng 3 v\u00e0 thua 3 \u1edf 6 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n- Roma th\u1eafng k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 3 tr\u1eadn, h\u00f2a 1 v\u00e0 thua 2 \u1edf 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n- Theo k\u00e8o ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Real th\u1eafng 5 v\u00e0 thua 3 \u1edf 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Roma v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n- Real Madrid \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Roma c\u1ea3 2 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (C\u00fap C1 2015/16)<br>\r\n- Real Madrid th\u1eafng 1 (Juventus), thua 1 (MU) t\u1ea1i ICC 2018<br>\r\n- AS Roma th\u1eafng 2, thua 1 sau 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 n\u00e0y<br>\r\n- 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Roma c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 22 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 3 b\u00e0n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p nhau g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa hai CLB v\u00e0 4/7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 3 b\u00e0n. Vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt do m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadn k\u1ec1 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nReal Madrid: Navas; Carvajal, Vallejo, Nacho, Theo; Llorente, Kroos; Bale, Ceballos, Isco, Asensio<br>\r\nAS Roma: Olsen; Florenzi, Manolas, Marcano, Santon; Pellegrini, Strootman, De Rossi; Kluivert, Faraone, Dzeko<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5215","checkdouble":"193968"},{"date":"19:34 07/08","title":"\u201cBom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/28/sevilla-muon-co-batshuayi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sevilla mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Michy Batshuayi c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Batshuayi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Michy Batshuayi kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Chelsea. Anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi Dortmund theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sevilla mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Michy Batshuayi \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sevilla mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Michy Batshuayi \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/29/Sevilla-muon-muon-Michy-Batshuayi-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Batshuayi mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBatshuayi ghi t\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n sau ch\u1ec9 13 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Bundesliga, phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Dortmund ng\u1ecf \u00fd mua \u0111\u1ee9t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a ra khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kham n\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, anh \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Olivier Giroud v\u00e0 Alvaro Morata, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Chelsea c\u0169ng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tammy Abraham, ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Swansea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, anh mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o trong tay, HLV Sarri s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ebft. \u00d4ng d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0\u00a0Batshuayi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sevilla mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Batshuayi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, Batshuayi \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, HLV Sarri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bom x\u1ecbt Chelsea s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Bom x\u1ecbt Chelsea s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/28/sevilla-muon-co-batshuayi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Batshuayi s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Sevilla</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-bat-ngo-muon-gay-soc-voi-batshuayi-180-192579.html\" target=\"_blank\">Atletico h\u1ecfi mua Batshuayi </span>nh\u01b0ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Valencia c\u0169ng v\u1eeba g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Sevilla mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Michy Batshuayi c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1\u00a0h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Batshuayi t\u1edbi Sevilla theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5214","checkdouble":"193959"},{"date":"22:27 07/08","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n M.U ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ec3 \u201ct\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5\u201d Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/tiet-lo-so-tien-mu-phai-chi-de-tong-co-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1eadn bao nhi\u00eau n\u1ebfu bay gh\u1ebf?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Premier League b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 HLV b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Jose Mourinho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra \u0111i s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t, v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 6/1 (\u0111\u1eb7t 1 \u0103n 6).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford, nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f2ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng, n\u1ebfu ch\u1eb3ng may 2 b\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi nhau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Man United s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 cho Jose Mourinho 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng &ndash; \u0111\u00fang b\u1eb1ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111ang nh\u1eadn, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sa th\u1ea3i ngay m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin cho th\u1ea5y Nh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn MU sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn MU sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Kha-nang-lon-MU-sa-thai-Mourinho-voi-dieu-khoan-dac-biet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn (th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng), khi CLB g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i Louis Van Gaal. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi Mourinho \u0111ang ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat ra b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Mourinho.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, s\u1ef1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u01a1n b\u00e3o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e0n ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho l\u1ea1i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-nhung-ngay-cuoi-172-193954.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-nhuong-mu-5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-nhung-ngay-cuoi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-nhung-ngay-cuoi-172-193954.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: 5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i</span><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-gianh-chien-thang-mourinho-duoc-yeu-cau-lam-dieu-bat-ngo-172-193670.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/de-gianh-chien-thang-mourinho-duoc-yeu-cau-lam-dieu-bat-ngo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-gianh-chien-thang-mourinho-duoc-yeu-cau-lam-dieu-bat-ngo-172-193670.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</span><br>\r\nSau nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, theo c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man United &ndash; Brian McClair.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5213","checkdouble":"193973"},{"date":"05:51 08/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Athletic Bilbao.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea kh\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Chelsea v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o t\u1eeb Real Madrid, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i. T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi Real b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh, anh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00e3 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u00f4i qua k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb h\u1ea1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, Courtois v\u1eabn b\u1eb7t v\u00f4 \u00e2m t\u00edn. K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u0169ng b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, Courtois g\u1eedi \u0111i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/Chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-Kepa-Arrizabalaga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n thi\u1ebft tha \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Courtois b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ra tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n duy tr\u00ec k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng dung t\u00fang h\u00e0nh vi n\u00e0y. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, The Blues c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nCh\u1ed1t mua Kepa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Telegraph m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Bilbao tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi The Blues bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea s\u1eafp ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB ch\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m khi \u0111\u01b0a Alvaro Morata v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ea3 ngay 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u00f9y th\u00e0nh t\u00edch. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a Kepa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng sau khi Liverpool chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson t\u1eeb Roma.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chelsea \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Kepa. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 k\u00e8o Real gia t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng trong \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Courtois. Los Blancos ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n chi 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (35 tri\u1ec7u Euro) trong khi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-muon-co-batshuayi-180-193959.html\">\u201cBom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-hy-vong-sarri-khong-kho-hieu-nhu-conte-172-193918.html\">Sao Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng Sarri kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga-172-193916.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barkley-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-193912.html\">\u201cSao x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5212","checkdouble":"193984"},{"date":"06:05 08/08","title":"V\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, Courtois b\u1ecb Chelsea \u201cl\u00f4i c\u1ed5\u201d ra ph\u1ea1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/22/vo-ky-luat-courtois-bi-chelsea-loi-co-ra-phat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb Chelsea. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong 2 ng\u00e0y qua v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o The Blues kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois quy\u1ebft r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, The Blues v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y. Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Courtois y\u00eau c\u1ea7u so v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, Courtois quy\u1ebft r\u1eddi Chelsea trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u00e0nh cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9. S\u1ed1t s\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid, nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 3 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Thibaut-Courtois-chuan-bi-nhan-an-phat-tu-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Courtois chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Real, Courtois kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho Chelsea. Sau khi th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh, anh l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00e3 2 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp qua, d\u00f9 h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p, Courtois v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. HLV Maurizio Sarri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai song kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea v\u1eeba ra ch\u1ec9 th\u1ecb Thibaut Courtois bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp v\u00e0o gi\u1edd \u0103n tr\u01b0a th\u1ee9 4 n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi Courtois chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb Chelsea, v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ea1t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois noi ve tuong lai\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Nong-HLV-Real-bat-ngo-che-Thibaut-Courtois-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi HLV Sarri r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ngh\u1ec9 t\u1eadp cho t\u1edbi khi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u00e1ng t\u1ecf. Song nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho khung g\u1ed7 trong th\u1eddi gian qua. Sau c\u00f9ng, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ed1t mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga-172-193984.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Kepa</span> tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Courtois, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho Courtois ch\u01b0a khi\u1ebfn Chelsea h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 13 trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng anh m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga-172-193984.html\">N\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-muon-co-batshuayi-180-193959.html\">\u201cBom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-hy-vong-sarri-khong-kho-hieu-nhu-conte-172-193918.html\">Sao Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng Sarri kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga-172-193916.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5211","checkdouble":"193985"},{"date":"06:28 08/08","title":"Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng cho M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/tottenham-da-dong-y-ban-trung-ve-khung-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho M.U. Tuy nhi\u00ean, CLB B\u1eafc London \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y cho t\u1edbi khi h\u1ecd t\u00ecm ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Alderweireld cho M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U. \u00d4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean mang v\u1ec1 1 trong 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean (ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea3 hai) Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Harry Maguire.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n c\u00e2n, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alderweireld l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 thi h\u01a1n v\u1edbi M.U. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Maguire v\u1edbi Leicester City. C\u0169ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf, Leicester quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ra \u0111i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng t\u1eeb M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-48,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho M.U v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau khi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trung v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Tottenham kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i Alderweireld cho M.U ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino\" title=\"HLV Pochettino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Mauricio-Pochettino-noi-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Pochettino ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Tottenham v\u1eabn \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm. H\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai v\u1ec1. S\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ed9 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Spurs l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u M.U l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Alderweireld.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 5 (9/8), M.U s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mang v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 trung v\u1ec7. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 Alderweireld, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 g\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona hay Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 Maguire v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u00f4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 Alderweireld hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u00ean gia nh\u1eadp, M.U c\u0169ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Marcos Rojo. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n tinh gi\u1ea3n bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho tr\u00ecnh l\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-mu-nen-mua-zaha-172-193931.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: M.U n\u00ean g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf s\u0129 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i Wilfried Zaha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cuc-lon-cho-thay-mu-chuan-bi-don-trung-ve-moi-172-193882.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea5y M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-pogba-da-tro-lai-man-united-172-193880.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-dua-ra-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-barca-172-193877.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho M.U, Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\">Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-mot-lan-nua-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-193826.html\">Willian: T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn MU ho\u1eb7c Real n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5210","checkdouble":"193988"}]}